      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>The inscription is in relief (0.1-0.2 cm high). The last letter on the second line is rough and ambiguous. The stone was found east of the town. In the first line, the author highlights the four-stroke sigma, which leads him to believe that this stone may come early in the Christian series.</p>
         </div>
